{"id": "1452161675347099658", "channel_id": "1452161675347099658", "type": 0, "author_id": "1048205315201581156", "author_name": "tourin.", "author_bot": false, "content": "(UID: 100409135)\n\n角的級數會直接性的影響到體質(血量)、角自己的攻擊與防禦基數\n角本身可直升60級\n3啟+8啟（人格深化）+5級\n\n滿啟（3啟+12啟）+5級\n以上只需要基礎物資", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T04:52:03.262000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-21T05:07:52.392000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1452161675682910453", "filename": "2025-12-21_124609.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 226384, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452161675347099658/1452161675682910453/2025-12-21_124609.png?ex=69cca473&is=69cb52f3&hm=b135e8c7e770aa2481bcaab11fc550caf8d3e76263aca0ee6a9c71c533cf6e5a&"}, {"id": "1452161676047683636", "filename": "2025-12-21_124609.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 226384, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452161675347099658/1452161676047683636/2025-12-21_124609.png?ex=69cca473&is=69cb52f3&hm=3eec8cad36ce971ceb9f832cc500dee6cbb4e70d4c759c59c123943c7ce34fd1&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452161675347099658", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人該知道的-角色升級方法(至90級)", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1452161817844514890", "channel_id": "1452161675347099658", "type": 0, "author_id": "1048205315201581156", "author_name": "tourin.", "author_bot": false, "content": "以下的升級方式可無視你的啟數來增加：\n\n單使用靈核，每個可+2級，最多可+10級", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T04:52:37.236000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452161817815290000", "filename": "2025-12-21_124509.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 71638, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452161675347099658/1452161817815290000/2025-12-21_124509.png?ex=69cca495&is=69cb5315&hm=0ffc398b62b18c2002fb1bc8dce0bd39d77a245cb3798ce2bec1a98295f82461&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452161675347099658", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人該知道的-角色升級方法(至90級)", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1452161960979337312", "channel_id": "1452161675347099658", "type": 0, "author_id": "1048205315201581156", "author_name": "tourin.", "author_bot": false, "content": "靈核已經用滿5個後，想再升就要靈核+精粹靈核，每組可+2級，最多+10級", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T04:53:11.362000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452161960064847875", "filename": "2025-12-21_124515.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 54340, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452161675347099658/1452161960064847875/2025-12-21_124515.png?ex=69cca4b7&is=69cb5337&hm=fb7d97c751d01f5020e0b5c0c29359fcab3746ca6758d1fddf03d2719fb32b1e&"}, {"id": "1452161960778006649", "filename": "2025-12-21_124509.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 71638, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452161675347099658/1452161960778006649/2025-12-21_124509.png?ex=69cca4b7&is=69cb5337&hm=28dc25b0c65593b486a378cf6f59d105fc2de1bb6e8a10d056cc2bb2979ab920&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452161675347099658", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人該知道的-角色升級方法(至90級)", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1452162062573633627", "channel_id": "1452161675347099658", "type": 0, "author_id": "1048205315201581156", "author_name": "tourin.", "author_bot": false, "content": "全過程都要知靈製劑，所以如果有任何活動所需以外多餘的靈啡肽，盡量能換知靈製劑就換，反正要升瘋狂預兆也是要用到（不如說總是卡在要需要知靈製劑的時候）", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T04:53:35.584000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1452162061818658928", "filename": "2025-12-21_124527.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 34074, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452161675347099658/1452162061818658928/2025-12-21_124527.png?ex=69cca4cf&is=69cb534f&hm=8b440e3ef92eb2aa6183e4cd01b9f2d75530f94f792a67d6e3f8aeeab9d4fd2e&"}, {"id": "1452162062271778826", "filename": "2025-12-21_124523.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 62370, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1452161675347099658/1452162062271778826/2025-12-21_124523.png?ex=69cca4cf&is=69cb534f&hm=04309a3cf16203cc56a697fe42d58f63358019308406d4d91b6d571799fc4b7d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452161675347099658", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人該知道的-角色升級方法(至90級)", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
{"id": "1452163783978913854", "channel_id": "1452161675347099658", "type": 0, "author_id": "1048205315201581156", "author_name": "tourin.", "author_bot": false, "content": "看到有人角色滿啟卻只有60級而有點崩潰的我寫了這篇，歡迎各語言大拿翻譯後往下貼各語文版本", "timestamp": "2025-12-21T05:00:25.999000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-21T05:02:21.215000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1452161675347099658", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人該知道的-角色升級方法(至90級)", "forum_channel_id": "1356200054276493444"}
